{"tid":1685914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台：警不必要武力阻正常採訪 憤怒並予最嚴厲譴責","createTime":"2019-10-31T23:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T00:23:48.000Z","uid":103981,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d0ea6d71f34280499f7e714d8c5e8dc38c6b2e","tid":1685914,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:54:56.000Z","msg":"本台攝影記者晚上在蘭桂坊附近採訪期間，被警員用盾牌推撞及用電筒照射。攝影記者向警員提出質疑，要求對方提供警員編號，隨即兩度被正面噴胡椒水，需要送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n港台發言人強調，本台記者當時身穿印有港台標誌的反光背心。對短時間內接連有記者在示威活動採訪期間，遭受現場警員以不必要的武力對待，導致受傷及阻撓正常採訪，港台表示憤怒，予以最嚴厲譴責 。<br />\n<br />\n港台再次呼籲警方尊重新聞自由及記者的合法採訪權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489387-20191031.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489387-20191031.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=d554e14d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489387-20191031.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bc21b5f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489387-20191031.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ce2df9f5abf7ef29b592e5e4e17ff7b7062a26bb","tid":1685914,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:57:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfe6f13c8ceaca384a428361f49342cf5c02ab20","tid":1685914,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e1de7a782217504b66a3fbcdf767f888e8f507","tid":1685914,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:58:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"024c80eaf22552b0b79e6a49a5b8798911398638","tid":1685914,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:58:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1637f5a27739523b442565806f3efccc8969e91","tid":1685914